text: Tschiertschen is a village in the municipality of Tschiertschen-Praden of the district of Plessur in the canton of Graubünden in Switzerland. The formerly independent municipality merged with Praden to form Tschiertschen-Praden on January 1, 2009. Category:Villages in Graubünden Category:Former municipalities of Graubünden
